The Unit shall renew the registration or registration certificate of each registrant or registered sales representative that:
submits to the Unit a renewal application on the form provided by the Unit;
would qualify for an initial registration or initial registration certificate;
for renewal of a registration, pays to the Division a nonrefundable renewal fee based on the number of building permits for the construction of new homes issued to the registrant in the preceding calendar year as follows:
10 or fewer new homes................................... $300; and
11 or more new homes....................................... $600; or
for renewal of a registration certificate, pays to the Division a nonrefundable renewal fee of $200; and
is otherwise entitled to be registered.
